=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_UGen_ex9 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_dark pure_tone sound, with complex oscillator character around 504 Hz, featuring punchy attack and sustained envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character, and spectrally simple.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: very_dark
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: pure_tone
  spectral_complexity_mean: simple
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 503.9684
  harmonic_decay_rate: -11.3284
  harmonic_regularity: 0.5912
  pitch_clarity: 23.8312
  inharmonicity: 0.0703
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -8.0097
  resonance_freq: 495.2637

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: UGen Example 9
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Classes/UGen.html
// Tags: UGen, Classes
// ---
// --- Example 9 ---
{ SinOsc.ar(500 + LFPulse.ar(4).bipolar(40), 0, 0.5) * 0.1 }.play;
